<item>
            <title>[MNG-3023] Reactor projects should be included in dependency resolution</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-3023</link>
                <project id="12316922" key="MNG">Maven (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Dependency resolution for mojos with @requiresDependencyResolution should include the projects within the reactor.  See attached it0122 for an example (numbered as such due to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-2994&quot; title=&quot;Snapshot repositories are not checked when using ranges&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MNG-2994&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MNG-2994&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&apos;s it0121).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12797365">MNG-3023</key>
            <summary>Reactor projects should be included in dependency resolution</summary>
